               <p>THOMAS ROBINSON. I am a <rs id="t18260914-392-viclabel2197" type="occupation">tallow-chandler</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-392-victim2036 t18260914-392-viclabel2197"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18260914-392-crimeloc2198">Drury-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-392-crimeloc2198" type="placeName" value="Drury-lane"></interp>
